Name: assign_team_to_project
Description: Whether a team is assigned to a project

Name: assign_worker_to_team
Description: Whether a worker is assigned to a team

Name: assign_user_story_to_sprint_backlog
Description: Whether a user story is placed into a sprint backlog

Name: select_feature_for_release
Description: Whether a feature is included in a release plan

Name: choose_scrum_master_for_team
Description: Whether a Scrum Master is linked to a team

Name: choose_product_owner_for_backlog
Description: Whether a Product Owner manages a backlog

Name: prioritize_user_story
Description: Assigned priority (discrete scale) for a story

Name: allocate_budget_to_project
Description: Budget amount allocated to a project

Name: set_story_points
Description: Story points assigned to a user story
